short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: No more todos, just get stuff done. Using this extension you can build momentum throughout your day by getting things done.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Finally another todo list!" - no one ever

Instead, we introduce you to the done list! Celebrate the progress you make throughout the day, instead of overwhelming yourself with more things that you have to get done. 

Don't worry, we've included a simple todo list as well.
